==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Illegitimation
<hw>Il`le*git`i*ma"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The act of illegitimating; bastardizing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The state of being illegitimate; illegitimacy.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Gardiner had performed his promise to the queen of getting her
<qex>illegitimation</qex> taken off.</q> <rj><qau>Bp.
Burnet.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Illegitimatize</ent>⟦br⟧
